@startuml
title UML State Chart Diagram



state StartChoice <<choice>>

state Login
Login : entry / user provide Login Details
Login : do / verify Data
Login : exit / login Successful

state "Main Area" as MainArea
MainArea : entry / show Main Area
MainArea : do / allow to choose options
MainArea : exit / continue using service

state MarketConditions
MarketConditions : entry / show market conditions
MarketConditions : do / provide details on market report
MarketConditions : exit / continue using service

state PestControlHelp
PestControlHelp : entry / user select pest control help
PestControlHelp : do / require photo and show techniques
PestControlHelp : exit / continue using service

state SoilSuggestions
SoilSuggestions : entry / receive soil information from user
SoilSuggestions : do / provide suggestions on suitable crops
SoilSuggestions : exit / continue using service

state WeatherInsights
WeatherInsights : entry / receive location from user
WeatherInsights : do / provide weather insights
WeatherInsights : exit / continue using service

state LabourAvailability
LabourAvailability : entry / receive location from user
LabourAvailability : do / show labour availability details
LabourAvailability : exit / continue using service

state Logout
Logout : entry / end session
Logout : do / terminate the session
Logout : exit / end


[*] --> Login
Login --> MainArea
MainArea --> MarketConditions
MarketConditions --> MainArea
MainArea --> PestControlHelp
PestControlHelp --> MainArea
MainArea --> SoilSuggestions
SoilSuggestions --> MainArea
MainArea --> WeatherInsights
WeatherInsights --> MainArea
MainArea --> LabourAvailability
LabourAvailability --> MainArea
MainArea --> Logout

Logout --> [*]

@enduml
